2014;;Hellion;;American;;Kat Candler;;Aaron PaulJuliette LewisJosh WigginsDeke Garner;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hellion_(film);;Thirteen-year-old Jacob's increasing delinquent behavior forces Child Protective Services to place his little brother, Wes, with his aunt. Jacob and his emotionally absent father, Hollis, must finally take responsibility for their actions and for each other in order to bring Wes home.